manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: WONDERFUL PULLBACK AIRPLANE MODEL TOY SOUND AND LIGHT Press the button to light up and make sound, it will surely pleasure your dear one. PULL BACK FUCTION Press the toy and then pull it back. PREMIUM QUALITY Delicate model with smooth plane body, which is friendly to children. Easy to grip and play. DIE-CAST AIR PLANE Most parts of this plane are made of metal, so it will be a little bit heavy for kids. However, it’s durable enough for long time playing. Good toys for family time. Parents can enjoy this cool toy plane with children and make more fun. Improve children’s hands-on ability and exercise their logical thinking ability. Promoting children's intellectual development.

Diecast plane toy Material: High grade zinc alloy + plastic Plane Size: 8.6 x 8.6 x 2.7 inches (22 x 22 x 7 cm) Color: Light-grey Battery type: Button Cell LR1130/AG10 Battery Quantity: 3 x LR1130/AG10(Included)

Die-cast plane Sturdy and non-toxic model can entertain kids for a long time. Endless of fun There are some military vehicles in it. When you press the button, you can see it, Meanwhile, sound and light can be actived. Pull back fuction Press the toy and then pull it back, after releasing, it will go forward a distance.
How to light up and make sound? Remove the battery card from its slot. Gently press the front wheel of the airplane.

NOTICE: Due to tiny parts, not suitable for children who are under 3 years old. This product contains electronic components that it can not be used in water or in damp environment. The color of the plane logo may be vary.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 6, 2022
reviews.reviewText: My 5 year old son loves this toy!!! Toy is very well worth the money,its a super cool airplane, you cannot control the volume for the sounds it makes but thats no problem at all because the sounds are not loud and thats a big plus,I don't like loud,annoying toys lol. I would totally buy thus toy again if needed...

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome Toy Plane
reviews.reviewText: This thing is seriously so cool. My husband is a KC-10 pilot and I am a KC-135 pilot. Our 3 year old son is OBSESSED with airplanes so we own more toy airplanes than anyone would consider normal. This little c-17 is so cute. It has a cool cargo compartment, lights, sounds and the overall quality is excellent. I was a little worried that this wouldn’t meet our expectations due to the lack of reviews but the quality is excellent, made a great stocking stuffer, and a high five for military planes. If only we can see a tanker next :)
